      "rationale": "Testing was conducted at a single quasi-static loading rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717. Only one test condition was evaluated; dynamic or fatigue loading conditions were not included in this validation activity. Achieved level 2 is below required level 3; this gap is noted and accepted given the static nature of the regulatory submission use case. This factor is the sole below-threshold item in the assessment."
